B.Mf=new A.J(B.Y,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Tip","Time signal words give away the tense:\n\u2022 **now / currently / at the moment** \u2192 present continuous\n\u2022 **always / usually / every flight** \u2192 present simple\n\u2022 **at 14:32 / yesterday / last night** \u2192 past simple\n\u2022 **while / when / as** \u2192 look for two simultaneous past actions\n\nAviation logs and reports always use **past simple** \u2014 they record completed events.",null,null,null)
